casebody.data:
Rafaela A. GUICHARDO, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
NEW JERSEY PROPERTY-LIABILITY INSURANCE GUARANTY ASSOCIATION (NJPLIGA), Defendant-Respondent. C-3 September Term 2018
080791 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 12, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004410-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
